<% content_for(:body_attributes) do %>
    data-no-turbolink="true"
  <% end %>

<div class="page-header">
  <h2>
    Trip
  </h2>
  <div class="fb-share-button" data-href="https://enerlet1.herokuapp.com" data-layout="button_count" data-mobile-iframe="true"></div>
</div>

<div class="jumbotron">
  <h1>Help the planet. One trip at a time.</h1>
  <p>Use our trip feature to travel greener. Enter in an origin and destination, and see what transport modes have the lowest carbon impact.</p>
</div>

<form class="form-horizontal" action="/trip/map">
  <div class="form-group">
    <label for="origin" class="col-sm-2 control-label">Origin</label>
    <div class="col-sm-10">
      <input type="text" class="form-control" id="origin" name="origin">
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="form-group">
    <label for="destination" class="col-sm-2 control-label">Destination</label>
    <div class="col-sm-10">
      <input type="text" class="form-control" id="destination" name="destination">
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="form-group">
    <div class="col-sm-offset-2 col-sm-10">
      <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Tell me the greenest mode</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</form>

<hr>

<div>
  <p>Thank you for visiting us. We would love to hear your comments. It will help us shape what EnerLet eventually becomes. <a href="http://chicagobooth.az1.qualtrics.com/SE/?SID=SV_8jhUtSpgq44FNA1" target="_blank">Click here</a> to submit feedback.</p>
</div>

